      "author": "james_MA (James West-Herr)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>I have a task.  Within the task is a checklist of items.  I want to include bulleted lists within the checklist, but when I try to assign the bullet style to the text within the checklist, it changes the  entire checklist to bullet.  Is this possible and if so, how?</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 142464,
