      "createdAt": "2023-09-07T17:12:48.667Z",
      "author": "Soroh (Soroh Donn)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Select that line and change it to bullets. It’s not working?<br />\n<img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/0/b0ef76a265f8a5f099373e3d91604e6c731e9da8.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"184\" height=\"154\" /></p>"
