      "id": 142484,
      "postNumber": 3,
      "createdAt": "2023-09-07T18:56:17.361Z",
      "author": "james_MA (James West-Herr)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Correct.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/0/a0df45245ba0a84c70eb0d5d607d513560e40693.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/a/0/a0df45245ba0a84c70eb0d5d607d513560e40693_2_690x247.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"247\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">941×337 37.5 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>I want the list within the checklist to read with bullets.  I’m able to get them all on their own line using shift-enter:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/9/b9d1b4d54ade848dfc2da09143f1f41b95102a6c.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/9/b9d1b4d54ade848dfc2da09143f1f41b95102a6c_2_690x409.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"409\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">914×542 45.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>but when I select the list and click on the bullet style, it turns into this:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/1/c/1ca7d5c245eac93b9b945ceff602ef42d84b2d00.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/1/c/1ca7d5c245eac93b9b945ceff602ef42d84b2d00_2_690x401.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"401\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">924×537 44.6 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>If I press the bullet button again, the checklist turns into a single bullet entry:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/7/7/774eb7b5f80aee849ab8a823ddd9573b558f58cf.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/7/7/774eb7b5f80aee849ab8a823ddd9573b558f58cf_2_690x399.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"399\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">923×535 44.6 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>thanks for your help!</p>"
